node.text:
I’m super excited to introduce the release of JɆ₮₱₳₵₭₴ in special collaboration with Jadu, one of the leading innovators of holograms and creators of the Mirrorverse. JɆ₮₱₳₵₭₴ are the first fully functional three dimensional (3D), augmented reality (AR), non-fungible tokens (NFTs). I’ve been engrossed in this world for almost a year, helping to curate and release NFTs for some of my favorite artists. Now, I’m thrilled to present my Genesis Drop to the world!! 

Many of you are already familiar with the rise of NFTs, while some of you are just becoming acquainted with digital art created through the blockchain. We are truly in the pioneering stages, and I welcome all of you to explore and ask questions as we learn together. The JɆ₮₱₳₵₭₴ we are releasing are 3D files, which can be transported into AR using our IOS app. This is an industry first! And here’s the best part, JɆ₮₱₳₵₭₴ can be used in conjunction with your individual avatar collection to jet around and interact with others in these worlds. This release ushers in a new era of NFTs, uniting communities like Meebit, Fluf, and VOID together.

Our version of the Metaverse, the Mirrorverse is here! These special NFTS are not only playable, but compatible between different worlds and have endless unimagined possibilities. Now you can purchase an NFT that interacts in our current app, but also in Metaverses yet to be created. Welcome to the next frontier of the digital entertainment economy! Our JɆ₮₱₳₵₭₴ generate fun, bridge communities together, and are interoperable between a myriad of digital worlds. 🚀

node.text: It is the individuals task to differentiate themselves from all the others and stand on their own feet. All collective identities interfere with the fulfillment of this task. Such identities are shields for the timid, beds for the lazy, and safe havens for the irresponsible.

node.text: School, politics, sports, and religion train us to compete against others. True rewards  (love, health, wealth, knowledge & equanimity ) come from ignoring competition and improving ourselves.
